query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(cn k mc mk t ml) NoMergeJoin(cn k mc mk ml t lt) NoMergeJoin(cn k lt mc mk ml t ct) */ select min(cn.name) AS from_company,
min(mc.note) AS production_note,
min(t.title) AS movie_based_on_book
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'violence',
'carving-a-pumpkin')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2009
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND ( cn.name like '20th Century Fox%' OR cn.name like 'Twentieth Century Fox%')
inner join movie_link AS ml
on ml.movie_id = t.id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join link_type AS lt
on lt.id = ml.link_type_id
inner join company_type AS ct
on mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind IS NOT NULL AND ct.kind <> 'production companies';
